				<h2>Convert Twist from frame B to frame A</h2>
<p>(full disclosure: this is homework)</p>

<p>I have a twist expressed in frame B:</p>

<p>$\zeta_b = \begin{bmatrix}1\\3\\-2\\0\\-2\\4\end{bmatrix}$</p>

